<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major World Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 18 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 11 major
world cities from 20:00 today to 20:00 on April 19 issued by China
's Central Meteorological Station tonight:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. 11 degrees C., max. 18 degrees C., cloudy to
drizzle, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Tokyo: min. 9 degrees C., max. 20 degrees C., clear to cloudy,
calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Bangkok: min. 25 degrees C., max. 32 degrees C., thunder
showers, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Sydney: min. 18 degrees C., max. 23 degrees C., cloudy, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
