<HEADLINE> China Opens Real Estate Website </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 18 (Xinhua) -- HomePRC.com, a new website
providing nationwide real estate market information, was
inaugurated today here.
</P>
<P>
According to Liu Jun, chairman and CEO of HomePRC, the new
website was established to create a platform for the buying and
selling of real estate property, and to provide a secure and
reliable e-commerce platform for the real estate industry.
</P>
<P>
