Real Estate News, the largest and most authoritative real estate
industry newspaper in China.
</P>
<P>
"We will launch our first overseas site in Hong Kong this year,
" he said, adding that the English version of HomePRC will also be
established to service overseas customers by the end of this year.
</P>
<P>
