will pay an official visit to China from April 24 to 29, at the
invitation of Chinese Foreign Minister Tang Jiaxuan, Sun announced.

Sixth China-ASEAN Senior Officials Meeting to Be Held in Malaysia
</P>
<P>
-- The sixth China-ASEAN Senior Officials Meeting (SOM) will be
held at Kuching of Malaysia from April 25 to 26, Sun announced.
</P>
<P>
-- The Chinese government demands that the United States
government prohibit all sales of advanced weapons to Taiwan,
including the Aegis-armed destroyer and long-range radar, Sun said
at the press conference.
</P>
