office at about 08:15 p.m. (local time) and just leaving the
office at around 02:20 p.m. (local time).
</P>
<P>
Rukmana was one of the treasurers of the Gotong Royong
Foundation chaired by Soeharto.
</P>
<P>
The AGO last week issued a warrant of travel ban to Soeharto
and put the former president under city arrest in its bid to
prevent him from leaving the country.
</P>
<P>
Soeharto now has been facing charges of corruption, collusion
and nepotistic practices when he was in power.
</P>
